# Lumina Care — Code Owners
#
# This file defines review ownership for the repository.
# Rules are matched top-to-bottom; the LAST matching rule wins.
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Enforcement requires branch protection to be configured with
# "Require review from Code Owners" in GitHub repository settings.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default owner — catches everything not matched below
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                   @moisesandradee

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CI / CD — workflows must be reviewed by the repo owner
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/                           @moisesandradee
/.github/workflows/                 @moisesandradee
/.github/CODEOWNERS                 @moisesandradee

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PhantomSeal — isolated cryptographic signing subsystem
# Any change here affects chain-of-custody evidence generation
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/phantom-seal/                      @moisesandradee
/.github/workflows/python-app.yml   @moisesandradee

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Backend API — FastAPI service
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/src/api/                           @moisesandradee

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend — Next.js web application
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/src/web/                           @moisesandradee

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Governance & operational docs — source of truth
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/LICENSE                            @moisesandradee
/SECURITY.md                        @moisesandradee
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                 @moisesandradee
/CONTRIBUTING.md                    @moisesandradee
/docs/REPO_STATUS.md                @moisesandradee
